    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#oliverio1927"/>, p. <citedRange>157</citedRange></bibl> (mention of find);
                    <bibl><ptr target="#oliverioTacc"/>, <citedRange>XI.49</citedRange></bibl>, whence
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SECir"/>, <citedRange>58</citedRange> (ph.)</bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>096300</citedRange></bibl>. 
                    </p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-62731"><name nymRef="#Ἀλέξανδρος">Ἀλέ<supplied reason="lost">ξ</supplied>ανδρος</name> 
                        <persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-65256"><name type="patronymic" nymRef="#Παραιβάτας">Παραιβάτα</name></persName></persName>
                    <lb n="2"/><w lemma="ἀνατίθημι"><supplied reason="lost">ἀ</supplied>νέθηκε</w>
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p>Alexandros fils de Paraibatas a consacré <supplied reason="subaudible">ce monument</supplied>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Alexandros son of Paraibatas dedicated <supplied reason="subaudible">this monument</supplied>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Alexandros figlio di Paraibatas ha dedicato <supplied reason="subaudible">questo monumento</supplied>.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
	       <p>Both fragments are now pasted together.</p>
	       <p><bibl><ptr target="#oliverio1927"/></bibl> dated the inscription of the third century BC, which seems too late for the lettering.</p>
            </div></body>
